Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:22.58,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Where does the truth lie for us？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:29.34,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}象徴を失って迷い始める大衆よ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.97,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Trust in everything that you believe,
